rows.label: tlk41100141_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I had to leave my island because it
got caught up in a conflict between
Invidia and Superbia.

rows.label: tlk41100141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Vandham helped us out, but I hear
some of the others went to Acedia.

rows.label: tlk41100141_03_msg0003
rows.name: I wonder which of us is happier now?

rows.label: tlk41100141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Although... Acedia seems like a better
place, all in all.

rows.label: tlk41100141_03_msg0005
rows.name:
It's a city, and it's well protected by
Pope Marveni, right?

rows.label: tlk41100141_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I don't trust grown-ups, but the
Pope? I think he's different.
